{"tid":2080083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息人士指，該名抽血員當日只有佩戴迷你黃色頭盔掛飾，並無涉及任何侮辱性字眼","createTime":"2020-06-26T07:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T11:26:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":715,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"5c05c3d7ac7c4e6ef586d1a25f64e845cdf4caff","tid":2080083,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"網傳日前一批警務人員23日在九龍灣輔警總部捐血時，有紅十字會抽血人員佩戴寫有「黑警死全家」、「對抗警暴」等字眼的飾物，惹在場警員不滿，警方要求紅十字會提供相關人員名字及職銜，但被拒絕，最終暫停有關捐血活動。有消息人士指，該名抽血員當日只有佩戴迷你黃色頭盔掛飾，並無涉及任何侮辱性字眼，批評紅十字會應為職員澄清，又質疑警員上綱上線，「如果巴士前後左右都有戴掛飾佢咪要跳落車？」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》已向紅十字會和警方查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200626&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61099209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200626%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61099209&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=62eb80fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200626%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D61099209&h=ca6095e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200626&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=61099209</a>"},{"pid":"096d06d08e594952ba1bff63cf7c6d62c38c18a1","tid":2080083,"uid":263086,"like":88,"dislike":1,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又質疑警員上綱上線</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67280465a438889318418d4dcaba089616db3b56","tid":2080083,"uid":27520,"like":244,"dislike":0,"score":244,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"「如果巴士前後左右都有戴掛飾佢咪要跳落車？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afe9f1f1c00259ffe0027663684eb269190407e","tid":2080083,"uid":226955,"like":291,"dislike":0,"score":291,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020